---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="zh-TW" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/lab-logo.png" />
  <title>關於實驗室 | iCPS Lab 智慧網宇實體系統實驗室</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-[#f8fafc] text-slate-800 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-blue-200 selection:text-blue-900 relative flex flex-col min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">

  <!-- ============================================================ -->
  <!-- 🔒 導覽列：原版不動                                          -->
  <!-- ============================================================ -->
  <nav class="w-full bg-white border-b border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative z-30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 flex items-center justify-between py-3 md:py-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8 min-w-0">
        <a href="https://www.nkust.edu.tw/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
          <img src="/images/nkust-logo.png" alt="NKUST 國立高雄科技大學" class="h-6 sm:h-9 md:h-10 lg:h-11 w-auto object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/4/46/National_Kaohsiung_University_of_Science_and_Technology_logo.svg/800px-National_Kaohsiung_University_of_Science_and_Technology_logo.svg.png';" />
        </a>
        <div class="h-4 sm:h-6 md:h-8 border-l-[1.5px] border-slate-300/80 shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
          <img src="/images/sicp-logo.png" alt="iCPS Lab 智慧網宇實體系統實驗室" class="h-7 sm:h-11 md:h-12 lg:h-[3.25rem] w-auto object-contain" onerror="this.style.display='none';" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 shrink-0 ml-4">
        <a href="/" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>首頁</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">Home</span></a>
        <a href="/about" class="group flex flex-col items-center text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>關於 iCPS Lab</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-blue-600">About</span></a>
        <a href="/#news" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>最新消息</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">News</span></a>
        <a href="/activities" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>活動花絮</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">Events</span></a>
        <a href="/#videos" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>影音專區</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">Media</span></a>
        <a href="/achievements" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>成果榮譽</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">Achievements</span></a>
        <a href="/members" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>實驗室成員</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">Members</span></a>
        <a href="/faq" class="group flex flex-col items-center hover:text-blue-800 transition border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-blue-800 pb-1"><span>常見問題</span><span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-600">FAQ</span></a>
      </div>
      <button id="mobile-menu-btn" class="md:hidden p-2 text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition focus:outline-none" aria-label="打開選單">
        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path id="hamburger-icon" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="mobile-menu" class="hidden md:hidden absolute top-full left-0 w-full bg-white border-b border-slate-200 shadow-lg flex flex-col z-20">
      <a href="/" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">首頁</a>
      <a href="/about" class="block px-6 py-4 text-blue-800 font-bold bg-blue-50">關於 iCPS Lab</a>
      <a href="/#news" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">最新消息</a>
      <a href="/activities" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">活動花絮</a>
      <a href="/#videos" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">影音專區</a>
      <a href="/achievements" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">成果與榮譽</a>
      <a href="/members" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">實驗室成員</a>
      <a href="/faq" class="block px-6 py-4 text-slate-600 font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-blue-800">常見問題</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============================================================ -->
  <!-- ✨ 頁面 Hero：內容重新設計                                    -->
  <!-- ============================================================ -->
  <header class="relative min-h-[520px] lg:min-h-[600px] overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 border-b border-slate-800">
    <canvas id="hero-canvas" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-80 pointer-events-none"></canvas>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_25%,rgba(37,99,235,0.28),transparent_32%),radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_20%,rgba(14,165,233,0.18),transparent_34%),linear-gradient(135deg,#020617_0%,#0f172a_52%,#071327_100%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.035)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.035)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:56px_56px] opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#f8fafc] to-transparent"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-28 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-36">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 rv rv-left">
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-blue-200 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full backdrop-blur-md mb-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
          <p class="text-blue-300 font-black tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-xs sm:text-sm mb-4">About iCPS Lab</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
            把 AI 研究，<br />
            做成能被現場使用的<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 via-cyan-200 to-white">系統</span>。
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-7 text-slate-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            智慧網宇實體系統實驗室聚焦 AIoT、邊緣運算、智慧醫療與智慧製造，從資料感測、模型設計到系統落地，打造能回應真實痛點的跨域解決方案。
          </p>
          <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <a href="#mission" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-blue-950/30 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5">
              了解研究定位
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:allenchang@nkust.edu.tw" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-white/15 backdrop-blur transition hover:-translate-y-0.5">
              合作洽詢
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5 rv rv-right rv-delay-200">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-cyan-500/20 blur-3xl rounded-[3rem]"></div>
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/15 rounded-[2rem] p-6 sm:p-7 shadow-2xl">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_20%,rgba(59,130,246,0.35),transparent_28%),radial-gradient(circle_at_85%_15%,rgba(34,211,238,0.18),transparent_30%)]"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.045)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.045)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:36px_36px] opacity-40"></div>

              <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.24em] uppercase mb-2">System Workflow</p>
                    <h2 class="text-white text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black tracking-tight">從資料到現場部署</h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500/20 border border-blue-300/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <div class="workflow-card group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/10 border border-white/10 p-4 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/15 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-cyan-400/15 border border-cyan-300/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-cyan-200 font-black">01</div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-white font-black text-lg">Sensing</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-0.5">感測資料、影像訊號、臨床與產線場域資料蒐集</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="relative ml-6 h-6 border-l border-dashed border-blue-300/30"></div>

                  <div class="workflow-card group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/10 border border-white/10 p-4 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/15 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-400/15 border border-blue-300/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-blue-200 font-black">02</div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-white font-black text-lg">AI Modeling</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-0.5">模型訓練、辨識判讀、決策邏輯與系統驗證</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="relative ml-6 h-6 border-l border-dashed border-blue-300/30"></div>

                  <div class="workflow-card group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/10 border border-white/10 p-4 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/15 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-400/15 border border-indigo-300/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-indigo-200 font-black">03</div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-white font-black text-lg">Edge Deploy</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-0.5">邊緣運算、即時回饋、現場導入與跨域應用</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-7 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950/35 border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
                    <div class="text-white text-2xl font-black">AI</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1">Research</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950/35 border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
                    <div class="text-white text-2xl font-black">IoT</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1">Sensing</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950/35 border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
                    <div class="text-white text-2xl font-black">Edge</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1">Deploy</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ============================================================ -->
  <!-- ✨ 網站主體：內容重新設計                                      -->
  <!-- ============================================================ -->
  <main class="flex-grow relative z-20 w-full">

    <!-- Sticky page tabs -->
    <div class="sticky top-0 z-20 bg-[#f8fafc]/85 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-slate-200/70">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-3 overflow-x-auto scrollbar-hide">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 min-w-max text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">
          <a href="#mission" class="page-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-700 hover:shadow-sm transition">實驗室定位</a>
          <a href="#pi" class="page-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-700 hover:shadow-sm transition">實驗室領航</a>
          <a href="#collaboration" class="page-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-700 hover:shadow-sm transition">合作與人才</a>
          <a href="#research" class="page-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-700 hover:shadow-sm transition">核心研究</a>
          <a href="#journey" class="page-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-700 hover:shadow-sm transition">加入我們</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 lg:py-24 space-y-24 lg:space-y-32">

      <!-- Mission -->
      <section id="mission" class="scroll-mt-28">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 rv rv-left">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
              <span class="w-10 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span>
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Lab Positioning</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-slate-950 tracking-tight leading-tight">
              不是單點技術展示，<br />而是完整系統解題。
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base lg:text-lg">
              iCPS Lab 的核心價值，是把人工智慧、感測資料與實體場域整合成可部署、可驗證、可持續改善的系統。研究從問題定義開始，最後回到醫療、製造與智慧城市等真實應用場景。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-7 rv rv-right">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <article class="process-card group bg-white rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 border border-slate-200/70 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                  <span class="font-black">01</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">感測資料</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">從影像、ToF、熱影像與感測訊號取得可信任的場域資料。</p>
              </article>
              <article class="process-card group bg-white rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 border border-slate-200/70 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 rv-delay-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-cyan-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                  <span class="font-black">02</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">AI 判讀</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">透過模型設計、訓練與驗證，把資料轉化為可解釋的決策依據。</p>
              </article>
              <article class="process-card group bg-white rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 border border-slate-200/70 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 rv-delay-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-slate-900 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                  <span class="font-black">03</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">系統落地</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">結合邊緣運算與人機介面，讓技術進入臨床、產線與實際場域。</p>
              </article>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-blue-950 rounded-[1.75rem] p-7 sm:p-8 overflow-hidden relative shadow-xl">
              <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
              <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-6 justify-between">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-blue-300 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-2">Research Philosophy</p>
                  <h3 class="text-white text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black leading-snug">從場域問題出發，讓研究成果被真正使用。</h3>
                </div>
                <a href="/achievements" class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-slate-900 px-5 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm hover:bg-blue-50 transition">
                  查看成果榮譽
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Principal Investigator -->
      <section id="pi" class="scroll-mt-28">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-stretch">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 rv rv-left">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[420px] rounded-[2.25rem] overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 shadow-2xl group">
              <img src="/images/professor-chang.png" alt="張萬榮 教授" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" onerror="this.src='/images/professor.png';" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950 via-slate-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute left-6 right-6 bottom-6">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-white text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase backdrop-blur border border-white/20 mb-4">Principal Investigator</div>
                <h2 class="text-white text-3xl font-black">張萬榮 教授</h2>
                <p class="text-blue-200 mt-1 font-medium">Wan-Jung Chang, Ph.D.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-7 rv rv-right">
            <div class="h-full bg-white border border-slate-200/70 rounded-[2.25rem] p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-50 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/3"></div>
              <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
                  <span class="w-9 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span>
                  <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Lab Leadership</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-slate-950 tracking-tight mb-6">跨域整合訓練，培養解題的工程人才。</h3>
                <blockquote class="relative pl-5 border-l-4 border-blue-500 mb-7">
                  <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    「工程教育的價值在於探索未知，並將科技回饋社會。我們期許團隊不僅掌握前瞻技術，更能為臨床與產業提出切實可行的解方。」
                  </p>
                </blockquote>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-7">
                  張教授深耕 AIoT 與邊緣運算多年，在高科大電子工程系建構高度跨域協作的研究環境。對外橋接醫療院所與科技產業，對內引導學生在紮實學理基礎上，將創意轉化為可驗證的系統成果。
                </p>

